re preparing for a lively M&A landscape in =E2=80=9925. Marion Maneker digs=
 into Sotheby=E2=80=99s abrupt volte-face on its controversial fee structur=
e. And Abby Livingston evaluates whether Elon Musk has already squandered h=
is political capital. On The Varsity,
